Description: Automated Red Hat ACM Hub Switchover Tool
 Automated, idempotent tool for switching over Red Hat Advanced Cluster
 Management (ACM) from a primary hub to a secondary hub cluster.
 .
 Features:
  - Pre-flight validation of hub clusters
  - Phased workflow with state tracking
  - Dry-run mode for safe testing
  - Post-activation verification
  - Support for passive-sync and full-restore methods
